These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
City: nizza, rome, hamburg
3 different pets are kept: lizard, hedgehog, ferret
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, havana, bluemaster
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, ship, airplane
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, balloon-flower, dahlia
3 different games are played: domino, poker, whist
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, amber, aquamarine
 1. the person driving the airplane is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person traveling to nizza is the havana-smoker##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 5. the person who likes lavender is the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| City      | nizza  | rome   | hamburg      |
| Pet          | ferret      | lizard     | hedgehog     |
| Cigar           | havana | bluemaster  | prince   |
| Transport   | ship   | airplane     | boat  |
| Flower   | marigold      | balloon-flower      | dahlia      |
| Game   | whist      | poker    | domino   |
| Color         | lavender    | amber | aquamarine |

