.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, february
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, tiparillo, bluemaster
House: cape-cod, cottage, gothic-revival
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, apricot, purple
There 3 different types of food: avocado, plum, artichoke
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, aconite
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, dubstep, indie
 1. the person who likes apricot is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating artichoke##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
10. the bluemaster-smoker is the person eating avocado##1
11. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday         | november | february  | august     |
| Cigar           | oliveros        | tiparillo | bluemaster    |
| House   | cottage  | gothic-revival    | cape-cod    |
| Color   | purple    | apricot    | brown   |
| Food           | artichoke        | plum    | avocado        |
| Flower         | amaryllis     | zinnia  | aconite     |
| Music-Genre     | indie         | dubstep       | jazz |

