.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, domino
House: tower, gothic-revival, farmhouse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, amaryllis
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, pink, ivory
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, video-games, hiking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, dubstep, reggae
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the tower house is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is the person playing domino##1
 7. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the fan of electronic is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Game      | domino   | canasta         | monopoly |
| House          | farmhouse  | gothic-revival        | tower    |
| Flower           | azalea | rose  | amaryllis  |
| Color   | ivory | coral | pink         |
| Hobby   | video-games | baking       | hiking        |
| Music-Genre           | electronic       | dubstep        | reggae       |
| Birthday     | may       | november  | january       |

