.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
House: cottage, farmhouse, gothic-revival
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, azalea, daffodil
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, cucumber, spinach
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, aristoff, bluemaster
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, chestnut
3 different games are played: poker, snooker, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, october
 1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes purple##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 6. the person eating cucumber is the person who likes chestnut##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| House      | gothic-revival   | cottage        | farmhouse           |
| Flower         | begonia | daffodil          | azalea      |
| Food           | broccoli   | cucumber | spinach |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | alhambra       | bluemaster         |
| Color   | purple    | chestnut          | lavender        |
| Game   | snooker  | backgammon        | poker     |
| Birthday         | february   | october         | november       |

