The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, van
3 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go
 1. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is in the middle##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person playing go is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
