.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter, train
City: colone, berlin, edinburgh
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, bridge
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, sunflower, poppy
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, green, brown
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, montecristo, oliveros
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, lawyer, traincher
 1. the traincher is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person who likes green is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 6. the person playing bridge is the game-smoker##1
 7. the lawyer is the game-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 9. the person who likes brown is in the middle##1
10. the traincher is in the middle##1
11. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Transport      | scooter       | snowmobile     | train         |
| City          | berlin      | colone  | edinburgh     |
| Game         | snooker | scrabble     | bridge |
| Flower   | iris  | poppy | sunflower     |
| Color   | lavender    | brown      | green     |
| Cigar   | montecristo  | oliveros    | game  |
| Job           | musician   | traincher      | lawyer      |

 